Detailed Description

Adapter that wraps both GCOS and Calvin cell file readers and contains the interfaces to the data.

virtual bool affymetrix_fusion_io::IFusionCELDataAdapter::ReadEx ( const char *  filename,
int  state 
) [pure virtual]

read cell file.

The state flag is used for GCOS files only.

Parameters:
filename Cell file name to read.
state [=CEL_ALL] Reading state
Returns:
If the read completed successfully. nState can be one or combination of the following values:

CEL_ALL Read all information in file (default)
CEL_DATA Read header and intensities only
CEL_OUTLIER Read header, intensities and outliers
CEL_MASK Read header, intensities and masked cells

Implemented in affymetrix_fusion_io::CalvinCELDataAdapter, and affymetrix_fusion_io::GCOSCELDataAdapter.
